56
00:04:03,327 --> 00:04:05,829
Went to election party 
on November, 3rd, 1992.

57
00:04:05,829 --> 00:04:08,833
Washed up on the bank of 
the Delaware the next morning
with a broken neck.

58
00:04:08,833 --> 00:04:10,882
Republicans thought
they had a bad night

59
00:04:10,882 --> 00:04:13,804
Best guess is she was tossed
from the Ben Franklin bridge.

60
